            <br> No Of Installments: {{loan.No_Of_Installments}}<br> Intrest Rate: {{loan.Intrest_Rate}}%<br> Total Amount: {{loan.Total}}<br> Installment Amount: {{loan.installments_set.first.Installment_Due|floatformat:2}}
